# profiles.yml is deliberately NOT ignored -- it holds no credentials (DuckDB = a local file
# path; BigQuery = method:oauth + an env var), and committing it is what makes `dbt build` work
# on a fresh clone. Real credentials live in gcloud's application-default store, outside the repo.
